item.title: CVE-2018-7802|2024-08-05T06:37:59.208Z -- schneider%20electric%20se -- evlink%20parking%20v3.2.0-12_v1%20and%20earlier
item.description: A SQL Injection vulnerability exists in EVLink Parking, v3.2.0-12_v1 and earlier, which could give access to the web interface with full privileges.

item.title: CVE-2018-7800|2024-08-05T06:37:58.855Z -- schneider%20electric%20se -- evlink%20parking%20v3.2.0-12_v1%20and%20earlier
item.description: A Hard-coded Credentials vulnerability exists in EVLink Parking, v3.2.0-12_v1 and earlier, which could enable an attacker to gain access to the device.

item.title: CVE-2018-7801|2024-08-05T06:37:59.388Z -- schneider%20electric%20se -- evlink%20parking%20v3.2.0-12_v1%20and%20earlier
item.description: A Code Injection vulnerability exists in EVLink Parking, v3.2.0-12_v1 and earlier, which could enable access with maximum privileges when a remote code execution is performed.
